						<div class="postbody">See <a href="http://esotericsoftware.com/" class="postlink">Spine</a> and <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aQy7eX_CWPM&amp;list=PL8Vej0NhCcI5sxOT64-Z31LW59VUyAVfr&amp;index=1" class="postlink">Spriter</a> for examples of software designed specifically for this. It's also sometimes called &quot;puppet animation&quot;.<br /><br />Fun image from <a href="http://danfessler.com/blog/thoughts-on-modular-animation" class="postlink">this blog post</a>:<br />puppet vs not.<br /><img src="https://i.imgur.com/3tGgvVQ.png" alt="Image" /></div>

					
